basic calls
Discworld Creator Help
basic calls

.SH How to list the quests a player has done
.SP 5 5
Once in a while you may need to check on whether or not a player has
completed a certain quest.  This is accomplished with:
.EP
.SI 5
%^CYAN%^pquests <player>%^RESET%^.
.EI
.SP 5 5
This will list all of the player's current quest information.
.EP

.SH How to grant a divorce
.SP 5 5
In rare cases, a player may approach you to ask about a divorce.
Most often this occurs when a player's MUD spouse is no longer active
on Discworld.  What this means is that it is impossible for them
to have a divorce granted via game channels.  To divorce a player:
.EP
.SI 5
%^CYAN%^call remove_property(\spouse\) <player>
dest wedding ring in <player>%^RESET%^.
.EI
